Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Geschichte Cimon und Pero (Caritas Romana)"

- Correspondence with Hugo Hedermann (dated 1955), with Weyer (dated 1954) and with Weigel (dated 1943)
- Extracts from different publications about 'Cimon and Pero'
- Article (reprint): 'Ein Rubens: Gemälde für das Museum des Siegerlandes' in "Siegener Zeitung" dated 28.03.1954
- Photocopies of reproductions of 'Cimon and Pero'
